title: Keep Speaking Victory | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Keep Speaking Victory | Joel Osteen
description:
You can't speak defeat and expect to see victory. When you use your words to speak faith, you'll usher in God's blessings, favor and abundance. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
